{dogName}. ")
print(f"{dogName} always wanted to go outside and explore {city}. ")
print(f"Today was {dogName}'s chance. The gate was accidently left
open! ")
print(f"{dogName} ran out the gate heading straight towards the city.
")
print(f"While walking down the street, {dogName} arrived at
{restaurant}. He always wanted to eat there. ")
